title: The Kry Discography 1992-2000 (5 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
THE KRY DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 5 releases...

 * 1992 - I'll Find You There
 * 1994 - You
 * 1995 - Unplugged
 * 1996 - What About Now
 * 2000 - Let Me Say

The Kry is a Christian rock/worship band from Quebec City, Canada. The band consists of Jean-Luc La Joie (vocals, electric and acoustic guitars, keyboards, some bass guitar) Yves La Joie, (drums, percussion, and backing vocals), Nic Rodriguez (bass guitar), Jean-Luc Lajoie currently serves on staff at Calvary Chapel Old Bridge located in Central New Jersey.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
